What is devops ?
"When the development team develops a software, it is handed over to the operations team for deployment and maintenance. DevOps helps both teams collaborate, automates the build, testing, and deployment process, bridges the gap between development and operations, and helps deliver software faster and more reliably."

How to install the ubantu in Windows 11?
Step_1 :- Open the powershell as a admin mode
Step_2 :- Type this command 
Command_1 : - dism.exe /online /enable-feature /featurename:Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux /all /norestart
Command_2 :- dism.exe /online /enable-feature /featurename:VirtualMachinePlatform /all /norestart
Step_3 :- Restart the system
step_4 :- Again Open the powershell as a admin mode
Step_5 :- Type this command 
Command_1 :- wsl --set-default-version 2
Command_2 :- wsl --install -d Ubuntu

Now we able to use the ubantu 
